    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Linux笔记-静态库与动态库]]></title>
    <link href="http://clivelee.github.io/blog/2013/12/27/linuxbi-ji-jing-tai-ku-yu-dong-tai-ku/"/>
    <updated>2013-12-27T13:43:31+08:00</updated>
